                    "message": {
                        "text": "Oracle.answerRequest(uint256,uint256) (../sb/Wallet_F.sol#127-165) uses timestamp for comparisons\n\tDangerous comparisons:\n\t- require(bool,string)(requests[id].active,Oracle: Request not active) (../sb/Wallet_F.sol#129)\n\t- require(bool,string)(! requests[id].answers[msg.sender],Oracle: Already answered) (../sb/Wallet_F.sol#143)\n\t- requests[id].requestTime < exchangeRateTime[symbol] (../sb/Wallet_F.sol#146)\n\t- (requests[id].answersCount * 100) / oracleList.length >= minimumQuorum (../sb/Wallet_F.sol#158)\n"
